name: Failed Registration - Email Already In Use
scenarioId: classpath:features/Register:Failed Registration - Email Already In Use
methodName: Failed Registration - Email Already In Use

testSteps.description: Given I am on the LinkedIn registration page
When I enters registration information with an already registered email address
And I clicks the "Join Now" button
Then I should see the system displays an error message stating that the email address is already in use

userStory.narrative:
As a user
  I want to create a new account
  so I will be able to access linkedin with my new account

title: Failed Registration - Email Already In Use
